runLouvain.R

runLouvain(res)

The Louvain clustering algorithm is employed to address the non-linear embedding in the latent space to produce multiple underlying cluster results to generate cluster ensemble.

Parameters:
res: default='1'
Attributes:
res: resolution

Example

run runLouvain.R:

R
source("runLouvain.R")
runLouvain(res=1)
